==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: rìchū ér zuò, rì rù ér xí
===Idiom===
'''[[日出]][[而]][[作]]，[[日]][[入]][[而]][[息]]'''
# Up when the sun is out, resting when its dark (as in the days of old).
